</td>
<td valign="top">
<ul>
<li>1994 <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Emblem_of_Tokyo.svg" class="image"><img alt="Emblem of Tokyo.svg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7f/Emblem_of_Tokyo.svg/23px-Emblem_of_Tokyo.svg.png" width="23" height="27" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7f/Emblem_of_Tokyo.svg/35px-Emblem_of_Tokyo.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7f/Emblem_of_Tokyo.svg/46px-Emblem_of_Tokyo.svg.png 2x" /></a> <a href="Tokyo" title="Tokyo">Tokyo</a>, Japan</li>
