<td class="navbox-abovebelow" style=";padding:0.2em 0.4em;line-height:1.25em;" colspan="3">
<div>
<div class="plainlist">
<ul style="">
<li style=""><sup><small>1</small></sup> <a href="Free_Imperial_City_of_Cologne" title="Free Imperial City of Cologne">Cologne</a> and <a href="Dortmund" title="Dortmund">Dortmund</a> were both capital of the Westphalian Quarter at different times.</li>
<li style=""><sup><small>2</small></sup> <a href="Antwerp" title="Antwerp">Antwerp</a> gained importance once <a href="Bruges" title="Bruges">Bruges</a> became inaccessible due to the silting of the <a href="Zwin" title="Zwin">Zwin</a> channel.</li>
</ul>
</div>
